#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:11275
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_STATUS_CREW\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"PROFILE: Vance Wentworth Prime\n"
"\t\t\tTitles: Leader of The Multiversal Rebellion, (Former) Federation Admiral, Veteran of The Mantis-Federation War, CEO of Wentworth Industries\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Human - Age: 75 - Gender: Male\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tVance Prime is a complicated figure. There's enough to be said about him to fill a whole library: he started the biggest insurrection the multiverse has ever seen, ruined the lives of countless people, and made an all-consuming monster in the Rebellion which cannot be contained or permanently stopped by this point. The fact that you agreed to give him a second chance either speaks to your compassion or your folly."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:11282
