msgstr "Leikonpliiinakra"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:11290
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_STATUS_CREW\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"PROFILE: Queen Leikonpliiinakra\n"
"\t\t\tTitle: Queen of the Mantis Hive\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Mantis - Age: 80 - Gender: Female\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tThe current queen of the Mantis Hive, Queen Leikonpliiinakra was the one responsible for allying the Hive with the Coalition, something she regrets but is unable to do much to reverse with the current economic crisis wrecking the Hive. Hopefully that can begin to change now."

