"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_STATUS_CREW\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"PROFILE: Cyra Black\n"
"\t\t\tTitles: Caretaker of the Protectorate, Original MFK Ace\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Human - Age: 74 - Gender: Female\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tOne of the two original MFKs, Cyra Black is the main person in charge of protecting the Protectorate and keeping Vance's nephew, Jerry Wentworth, safe and sound. She's extremely loyal to Vance and is his closest companion, second only to his nephew. They were close enough to the point of having an affair in the past."

