msgstr ""
"PROFILE: Leah Applebuzz\n"
"\t\t\tTitles: The Beam Master, Your Nemesis\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Human - Age: 24 - Gender: Female\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tThe daughter of Count Dinkleman Reichster Von Applebuzz Tri Tri the Fourth, and your personal nemesis. What she lacks in common sense and strategy, she more than makes up for in pure determination. It seems something you said to her has swayed her to your side, so now you two are problably more frenemies than nemeses."

