msgstr ""
"PROFILE: Michael Stepford\n"
"\t\t\tTitle: (Former) Mascot For Sammy The Spider\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Human - Age: 20 - Gender: Male\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tThe actor for Sammy The Spider, or at least he *was* the actor for the character until a close encounter with Stephan dressed as Ellie the Equinoid left him traumatized and unable to work for Flowers and Sunshine anymore. He got the gig thanks to playing Ellie at birthday party for Jerry Wentworth, Vance's newphew."

