"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_STATUS_CREW\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[6]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"PROFILE: Goziodeon Lar Auilacus\n"
"\t\t\tTitle: Leader of the Haunts\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Alpha Vagabond (More specifically a Poltergeist) - Age: 666 - Gender: N/A\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tThe Haunt's head honcho, the biggest and strongest criminal organization in this side of the Dynasty. Born just after the collapse of the Obelisk empire, Goziodeon enjoyed an early life of luxury and success in his family business before the Great Dynasty Depression hit, causing him to turn to a life of crime in order to survive. Turns out he had a knack for running criminal organizations, and in a few centuries managed to build an empire of crime that could match and surpass any pirate organization if only he ever dared to leave Specter territory."

