msgstr ""
"PROFILE: Stefan Richard\n"
"\t\t\tTitle: Minelauncher Salesman\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Human - Age: 42 - Gender: Male\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tThere's not much to say about Stefan. He inherited his minelauncher store in a quaint station in Federation territory; business was going well until a feak accident caused the station he lived and worked on to be transported across timelines, ending up in a land completely foreign to his own, filled with alien species he'd never heard of and weapons that made no sense to him."

