"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_STATUS_CREW\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[8]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"PROFILE: Jon Briggs\n"
"\t\t\tTitle: Lead Wentworth Technician, Multiversal Rebel\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Human - Age: 45 - Gender: Male\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tJon is one of the most well known technicians within Wentworth Innovations: his expertise when it comes to drones is unparalleled. In fact, drone booster technology was actually something he perfected. It is easily installed on any ships with high enough drone control levels without the need for any external augments. While he came to this universe from Universe 1, Jon's actual birtplace is unkown, implying that every Jon seems to make that decision in one point or another in their life."

