"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_STATUS_CREW\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[9]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"PROFILE: Clint Sheerman\n"
"\t\t\tTitle: (Now Former) Dread Pirate Purple Beard, (Former) Legionnaire Captain of the 45th Division, Pirate Legend\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Human - Age: 65 - Gender: Male\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tClint was born and raised in Universe 1. From a very young age, he was trained to be a Rebel soldier. He was taken from his family after turning 10 by Vance One himself and ever since then has trained every day to become a Legionnaire. While he did climb the ranks of the Legion very quickly, his career halted when he was forced to do an act that, to this day, he refuses to ever mention or elaborate upon. Whatever it was, it was so brutal that it broke his faith in the Rebellion. He faked his own death and fled Universe 1 by jerryrigging a MV drive to his trusty legion assault ship. Uninterested in joining any other faction, Clint turned to piracy, quickly making a name for himself and earning the moniker \"Purple Beard\". The rest, as they say, is history."

