msgstr ""
"PROFILE: Charlotte\n"
"\t\t\tTitle: Venomous Spider Queen\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Mutated Giant Alien Spider - Age: 20 - Gender: Female\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tWhile similar to the the regular Giant Alien Spider Queen, this specific specimen can excrete powerful venom which can easily incapacitate even the hardiest Rockman. She is unable to produce any eggs, however, so she can never create her own brood: a fact that might contribute to her affection for all things spider."

