"PROFILE: Slimer Ssstriel the 3rd\n"
"\t\t\tTitles: (Former) King of the Kleptocracy, Revenant Guard\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Revenant Slug - Age: 254 - Gender: Hermaphrodite (culturally male)\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tA old and now dead king of the Kleptocracy back when it was called the \"Collective Slug Kleptocracy\". His rule was so cruel that it caused the Kleptocracy to become a republic for almost 100 years. His death came thanks to food poisoning caused by a nasty batch of hallucinogenic melons, orchestrated by his own son."

