msgstr ""
"PROFILE: Phys Karvar\n"
"\t\t\tTitle: The Ion Shriker, Revenant Mascot\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Revenant Shell - Age: 151 - Gender: Female\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tThe Shell goverment once proposed a new research department that failed right after its inception. Phys, the first living test of their project, died shortly after being 'born' and took over the whole facility along with all of its research to make more of herself. She enjoys making others happy and is no longer in constant pain after being freed from her curse."

