"PROFILE: Aleenor Lakitrapikk\n"
"\t\t\tTitle: Mantis Bishop, Revenant Striker\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Revenant Mantis - Age: 210 - Gender: Female\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tOne of the most loyal Bishops chosen by Queen Latrakkpkat to be the caretaker of the hatchery in the deepest part of the Mantis Hive capital. Her life didn't consist of much besides her job, but she died protecting the eggs from the Great Hatchery Fire of the Silver Age, a tragedy that took the lives of millions of Mantis and could have ended the empire as a whole if not for Aleenor's quick thinking and sacrifice. Her name is still revered in the Mantis Hive and she even has a holiday dedicated to her."

