"PROFILE: Vin Vytredonn\n"
"\t\t\tTitle: Rock Paladin, Revenant Enforcer\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Revenant Rockman - Age: 450 - Gender: Male\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tA Rock Paladin who served and lived through a very peaceful period of the Rock Theocracy, his strength wasn't noteworthy and he didn't acomplish much in life. In fact, the most noteworthy thing about him was how he died. His autopilot went haywire while he was sleeping, sending him straight into a nearby red giant. Needless to say, he wasn't happy being bossed around by G."

