"\t\t\tTitle: MFK Ace, Revenant Listener\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Revenant Human - Age: 70 - Gender: Male\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tThe youngest revenant in G's team, and the least stable too. After his brutal death at the hands of a modified repair drone, this ex-MFK Ace is now just a shattered shell of who he once was. He wasn't a noteworthy Ace so his death was covered up by the Rebellion, his name becoming nothing more than a old legend to scare new recruits."

