"\t\t\tTitle: Revenant Right Hand\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Revenant Lanius - Age: ??? - Gender: N/A\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tThe first revenant and G's old friend. Their death is what caused G's spiral into necromancy in the vain hope of bringing them back to life. Now they only exist to extend G's will, serving her unconditionally. That is, until you broke her curse and saved them."

