"PROFILE: G The Necrolich\n"
"\t\t\tTitle: Revenant Leader, Necrolich, (Former) Obelisk Royal Navigator\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Revenant Obelisk - Age: Roughly 100000 - Gender: N/A (Culturally Female)\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tThe Obelisk Royal in charge of charting other universes, G was a loyal worker under Queen Y for all her life, and even in death she still hopes she can see her queen in person again. After the death of her close friend Zulu, G spiraled into a deep depression, unfortunately replaced by a dark ambition once she found the Necronomicon."

