"\t\t\tTitle: (Former) Sentinel, Revenant Preacher\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Revenant Crystal - Age: 580 - Gender: Male\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tA skilled Sentinel who had a bright future ahead of him until he was sent on a mission to recover a valuable Crystal weapon cargo from the hands of a strange gray ship, one that resembled the Utopians' work. But something about it changed Frostwall. His mind fell to the incessant whispers and he was put down shortly after."

