msgstr ""
"PROFILE: Deathbloom Y'Cirtil\n"
"\t\t\tTitle: (Former) Treasure Hunter, Revenant Seeker\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Revenant Oro'bache - Age: 208 - Gender: Female\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tDeathbloom's name might sound aggressive and murder-y, but the truth is that she was one of the kindest Vampweeds you could find outside of the Confederancy. In fact, she rarely even visited Vampweed-controlled sectors, usually only dropping in to sell her valuable artifacts. After her death, the system had to be quarantined as her spores somehow adapted to the vacuum of space and became deadlier each cycle. Now they are the deadliest biohazard known to the Vampweeds."

