msgstr ""
"PROFILE: Leonardo Lerpae\n"
"\t\t\tTitle: (Former) Eargen Enforcer, Revenant Spec-Ops\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Revenant Leech - Age: 149 - Gender:  Male\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tLeo never really wanted to be a fighter: in fact, his dream was to open a outpost that specialized in painting ships at low prices without sacrificing quality. Unfortunately, once the Republic started a war with the Theocracy, Leo was conscripted into the army and so his fate was sealed."

