"PROFILE: Searak Fray\n"
"\t\t\tTitle: (Former) Duskbringer, Revenant Bomber\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Revenant Zoltan - Age: 81 - Gender: Male\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tOne of the first Duskbringers to fight for the cause, Searak joined the movement after the death of his brother, Kirak, was glossed over during the original civil war, his name denied the valor of his sacrifice. After going mad thanks to Her influence, all the Duskbringer can see now is the pain and hatred he carried in life."

