"PROFILE: Augustus Goldicus Shinan the 5th\n"
"\t\t\tTitle: The Ghost With The Most, Revenant Exile\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Revenant Phantom Alpha - Age: 985 - Gender: N/A (Culturally Male)\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tThe richest Phantom in the universe, his endless scrap reserves are enough to buy a whole sector! Something which he *did* want to do before his own hubris brought his downfall after skimping on hundreds of safety regulations and perishing under the explosion of his own anti-bio weapons factory."

