"PROFILE: Sally Finch Morrey\n"
"\t\t\tTitle: (Former) Arcadia Scientist, Revenant Researcher\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Revenant Spider Experiment - Age: 90 - Gender: Female\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tSally was a brilliant biotech scientist who was close to developing a way of preventing crew skill degradation before a terrible illness took her life. However, just before she passed, she managed to upload her mind and consciousness into her Giant Alien Spider companion Finch. Now, with her human days behind her, she searches for her own place in this vast multiverse."

