msgstr ""
"PROFILE: Bellrennis \n"
"\t\t\tTitle: Lead Scientist In Commonwealth Exploration And Research\n"
"\t\t\tSpecies: Obelisk - Age: Roughly 90000 (at the time of death) - Gender: N/A (culturally female)\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tBellrennis, also known as Daisy, was the lead researching in weapons and drones for the Refuge. Her work was far superior to her peers but her ambitions were too great for the small place that was the Refuge. She wanted to explore the outside, to find allies for her people's cause. Her status as a potential security threat made her so controversial that it created a schism in the Refuge. She left the system but unfortunately didn't make very far before the Royals caught up with her, killing her and leaving her cruiser adrift as a grim reminder of their might."

