#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:12229
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_AUG_FR_SUPREME_HATRED\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Which buffs for you want to claim? All the possible bonuses are listed below.\n"
"\n"
"Nexus Notoriety: All weapons gain +10 shield piercing.\n"
"General Notoriety: +25% chance to resist damage to your systems and hull.\n"
"Union Notoriety: Your crew clones and heals 100% faster.\n"
"Harmony Notoriety: Your ship gains Auto manning level 2 and Auto repair.\n"
"Ministry Notoriety: Gain a stackable 10 hit point energy shield.\n"
"Free Mantis Notoriety: All friendly crew gain the free mantis pheromone ability.\n"
"Outcast Notoriety: All friendly crew gain hazard immunity.\n"
"Imperial Notoriety: Every time your ship takes damage, 2 shards will break off and fly at your enemy which pierces 2 shields.\n"
"Gathering Notoriety: Nullifies the ammo cost of weapons.\n"
"Confederacy Notoriety: You will gain 10 scrap every jump (not affected by Scrap/Repair arms).\n"
"Geniocracy Notoriety: All enemy crew and drones on-board will lose 10hp/s.\n"
"Commonwealth Refuge Notoriety: Full ion immunity and boosts standard shield charge rate by 150%.\n"
"Argeonn Reputation: Cooldown between weapon shots is improved by 25 percent.\n"
"Syndicate Reputation: Adds an option during jumpspeed that gives 10 fleet delay and fully maps the upcoming sector.\n"
"Tiiikaka Reputation: Makes each crew only use half their usual crew space."

